{"tid":1915842,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"pprb：我只要新聞稿到派下膠 黃絲就會忘記被捕手足","createTime":"2020-03-08T13:26:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T01:06:28.000Z","uid":32906,"like":118,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"24c0a1e45aa3f68832890228899516fada78a673","tid":1915842,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:26:42.000Z","msg":"今次2.6噸原料喎係咪都好好笑呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得上次揾到過百發子彈既屠龍小隊<br />\n今次係仲咪好笑過上次呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從有小隊比人殲滅<br />\n發新聞稿引公眾恥笑<br />\n再到公眾揾位笑黑警 笑自導自演 笑再吹大d呀⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n大眾成笑話睇 民憤就平息左好多<br />\n提番大家 屠龍其中一人在庭上覆述拘留期間被十隻狗關燈暴打 仲環押緊<br />\n<br />\n如果你既焦點放左係果2.6噸到<br />\n班小丑已經成功左<br />\n<br />\n但我一定唔會忘記"},{"pid":"53a3a0a87e57584be945c54f9103ca6cee86c405","tid":1915842,"uid":38633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce2a417aa49647aaa3e73164a3b5c23c8262c86","tid":1915842,"uid":32906,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yjEPwFE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyjEPwFE.png&h=50a8799a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁一隻手就拍唔響嘅<br />\n你睇啲&rsquo;手足&lsquo;幾配合"},{"pid":"41cedcf6dada64cf2e3ddd4529df0416763f1fd6","tid":1915842,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFXBbMG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFXBbMG.png&h=82c6be5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關心果2.6噸都唔關心果13個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd1d459b3564250d4c78ff5c341dcabf74db5ed","tid":1915842,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"琴晚：水晶之夜<br />\n今日：哈哈鳩